(25025, 'QwQ颓废团', 55, '# 为洛谷做贡献！！！\n\n\n## [我们的公共题库](https://www.luogu.com.cn/training/12934)\n\n---------------------------\n\n### $\\color{#FFA500}{\\text{我们的文章（学术区）}}$：\n1. [关于getline](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/QwQKonnyaku/guan-yu-getline)\n2. [CSP-J重点：BFS和DFS](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/3o6j5gzl)\n3. [01背包问题](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/214177/post-01-bei-bao-wen-ti)\n4. [关于高精度运算](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/9e3hje64)\n5. [C++中的常用集合：set](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/QwQKonnyaku/cpp-zhong-de-chang-yong-ji-he-set) \n6. [分解质因数&素数筛选法](https://kirito-2022.blog.luogu.org/Prime-factorization-and-Prime-screening)\n7. [贪心算法](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/CN-3ZMH3/tan-xin-suan-fa)\n8. [C++中STL容器：vector](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/02t37mk4)\n9. [矩阵学习笔记](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/BreakPlus/ju-zhen-xue-xi-bi-ji)\n\n10. [进制转换](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/5wurjp1d)\n11. [斐波那契前缀和解题记录](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/9bk1psby)\n12. [好玩的#define](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/267364/OI-define#)\n13. [简单数据结构](https://316443.blog.luogu.org/yi-suo-jian-dan-di-shuo-ju-jie-gou)\n14. [高精学习笔记](https://www.cnblogs.com/crab-in-the-northeast/p/high-precision.html)\n15. [广搜和差分](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/5y2d1n/guan-yu-guang-sou)\n16. [主席树](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/zvj9xjw0)\n17. [Floyd-Warshall](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/mantou/Floyd-Warshall)\n18. [【拓扑排序】学习笔记](https://www.luogu.com.cn/paste/unjyw5fo)\n19. [VMware虚拟机使用教程](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/ustinianx/vmware-using-instruction#)\n20. [$\\text{字典树（Trie树）}$](https://www.cnblogs.com/RadestionAdtinium/p/13164164.html)\n\n21. [洛谷网校 DAY 1-排序，枚举，模拟笔记](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/keduoli12/luo-gu-wang-xiao-day-1-pai-xu-mei-ju-mu-ni-bi-ji)\n\n22. [计算机发展史科普](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/keduoli12/ji-suan-ji-fa-zhan-shi-ke-pu)\n\n23. [二分和贪心笔记](luogu.com.cn/blog/keduoli12/luo-gu-wang-xiao-day-7-er-fen-hu-tan-xin-bi-ji-wei-geng-xin-wan-bi-post)\n\n24. [计算机发展史科普](https://www.luogu.com.cn/blog/keduoli12/ji-